name: APMS Status Report
query:
Select name  as "Service Order no:Data:150" ,date as "Date:Data:100",site_name as "Site Name:Data:200",service_nature as "Type of order:Data:100",service_status as "Service Status:Data:240" from `tabService Report`  
where date >=%(start_date)s and date<=%(end_date)s
